[~sjones]/[~tony]:

Issue looks to be fixed.  I had to change the cloudformation template to only create 99 security groups because there is one security group already created when a VPC is created (default).  Once I did that, everything worked like a charm.

Eucalyptus Version:  4.1.0-0.0.22975.327.20150113git527c000.el6

*Steps*

# Uploaded IAM access policy to group of given account:
{code}
